{"tid":2071210,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過DMZ板門店南北韓邊界","createTime":"2020-06-19T15:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T15:35:05.000Z","uid":223084,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0cf532282c9f37760f679cfe4af4daa739c070","tid":2071210,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"上google睇到D相好似想打咁<br />\n去之前又要簽生死狀"},{"pid":"aedb4ccce5e70e35308ba051b2d8b81912702e9d","tid":2071210,"uid":175930,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<br />\n首爾有旅行社代辦<br />\n但佢會有幾會當日美軍話唔開就冇得去<br />\n然後就帶你去望下北韓 博物館咁<br />\n所以好睇彩數"},{"pid":"439cb514889ca833518db09a8f90bd4b2b04154d","tid":2071210,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:19:21.000Z","msg":"呢排局勢比較緊張所以先要簽姐應該"},{"pid":"9b5a5393d9cf7efb9abc7d1d1468af66446d714b","tid":2071210,"uid":136216,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fb0cf532282c9f37760f679cfe4af4daa739c070","tid":2071210,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"上google睇到D相好似想打咁<br />\n去之前又要簽生死狀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:34:59.000Z","msg":"之前去過兩韓邊境分界線, DMZ 旅程由於時間不配合所以去不到，之前聽過就算join DMZ 旅行團，已現在兩韓關係這麼差和緊張都應該沒有旅行團能成行&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"62e70dd6065fd9af438b76c9a88b4ceb0acb4797","tid":2071210,"uid":119767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"以前study tour 有跟學校去 DMZ<br />\n係有條地洞路<br />\n行到一個位就唔行得<br />\n話再行過去就係北韓"},{"pid":"d3116d8933334f8289e69aa4258ad7e5d9d44742","tid":2071210,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:12:37.000Z","msg":"係要簽，果張野個名係聯合國<br />\n<br />\n搞一大輪又睇片又盛 ，去到限時影相，睇簽和約果個帳篷就冇<br />\n<br />\n佢話南北韓輪流站崗，好少見到對面，最多老遠見到<br />\n<br />\n跟住睇下博物館 地洞d 19野，番到去就日落"},{"pid":"8036fe3f7c85a5ac68751b440705276ba5f1f964","tid":2071210,"uid":86369,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:20:13.000Z","msg":"去過<br />\n去成日留得三個字左<br />\n不過南泡無嘢玩是鬼但啦"},{"pid":"2f9551573a0c22900a1011028d0bb94efb8f8dc0","tid":2071210,"uid":271714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T23:46:13.000Z","msg":"經北韓果邊去，接受左好長時間反美同大韓統一嘅猛烈宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3e07e26791dae6da4a64ca861eb76d1a000b63","tid":2071210,"uid":25322,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"分別係南韓同北韓入過三八線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓氣氛緊張好多 要簽紙同排好隊參觀 限制多d<br />\n<br />\n北韓就causal d 好似旅遊景點咁參觀 仲可以同軍官影相同偷signal上網 臨走前可以買反美poster tshirt<br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦 入到三八線參觀好講緣份 如果冇肺炎,依家咁嘅局勢一定入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3865f3f7f13467395c055587677cfb53086405","tid":2071210,"uid":41961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:29:10.000Z","msg":"上年尾豬瘟唔俾人入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e92e16dda9e01f195e4373ec54a67fadcf41c","tid":2071210,"uid":11553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"南韓要排隊成班on9學生咁<br />\n又話唔好著拖鞋短褲<br />\n會俾北韓影相做propaganda笑鳩南韓窮<br />\n<br />\n北韓hea好多，入到去自由浮動都冇咩問題"},{"pid":"239fb6343042746c53225e165f95ec54d398a903","tid":2071210,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:45:06.000Z","msg":"藍屋裡面個泡菜士兵<br />\n識扮佈景板企喺度唔郁唔笑<br />\n不過唔知如果引到佢笑會唔會俾佢打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1449d0fb8157a247c5108c56581c6ec3adafecf9","tid":2071210,"uid":112813,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"跟團去北韓時去過<br />\n入去前有一大堆舖頭比你買野，之後上旅遊巴，有個北韓軍人上車企係車頭望住前面，話保護團友安全，落車入屋仔，屋入面有地圖，屋入面個北韓軍人係咁講美國衰野，之後就睇同坐簽約張枱同櫈，然後上板門店望條38線，對面南韓揀建築物靚過香港既好撚多<br />\n最on9係我個日唔小心著件有美帝國旗既衫比導遊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要搵件褸禁住先去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b24e7c5312346a601adee9d8444129e64c87187","tid":2071210,"uid":21198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e3e07e26791dae6da4a64ca861eb76d1a000b63","tid":2071210,"uid":25322,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"分別係南韓同北韓入過三八線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓氣氛緊張好多 要簽紙同排好隊參觀 限制多d<br />\n<br />\n北韓就causal d 好似旅遊景點咁參觀 仲可以同軍官影相同偷signal上網 臨走前可以買反美poster tshirt<br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦 入到三八線參觀好講緣份 如果冇肺炎,依家咁嘅局勢一定入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"絲打見識真廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有機會我都想係南韓個邊參觀下<br />\n北韓反而無想像中咁緊<br />\n一包煙仔就可以哄掂啲士兵"},{"pid":"8de8ed5a3a61b02cfe97e29c1a91ac72af4751ac","tid":2071210,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439cb514889ca833518db09a8f90bd4b2b04154d","tid":2071210,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:19:21.000Z","msg":"呢排局勢比較緊張所以先要簽姐應該"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"平時去都要簽<br />\n而家應該唔開添"},{"pid":"e64102d0572deed9395a3809f05c2dbc0bf99157","tid":2071210,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e70dd6065fd9af438b76c9a88b4ceb0acb4797","tid":2071210,"uid":119767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"以前study tour 有跟學校去 DMZ<br />\n係有條地洞路<br />\n行到一個位就唔行得<br />\n話再行過去就係北韓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"我幾年前去過<br />\n就咁啱第三隧道唔開冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果要partial refund"},{"pid":"366d0b48224613bf5211049d2e8c619e62db8f3f","tid":2071210,"uid":14337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"試過由北韓過去 <br />\n去之前會瘋狂洗你腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年前想由南韓過去<br />\n但最後被人取消左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到宜家都好想由南韓過去睇"},{"pid":"918939bf7766281ed2f74cdefb742155a6fcd576","tid":2071210,"uid":168020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"冇去過 <br />\n<br />\n但之前去過江華島 又係好近北韓 <br />\n上去瞭望台會見到北韓開峰郡嘅一個邊境小陣 <br />\n見到有學校 有人 有屋企 仲見到有北韓人岀嚟散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去江華島睇呢個仲值得 肉眼睇好細粒 但有望遠鏡 同成班朋友睇到唔想走"},{"pid":"89b7c4d359acbf8054f10fc90f0d5358ec92178f","tid":2071210,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇去過 <br />\n<br />\n但之前去過江華島 又係好近北韓 <br />\n上去瞭望台會見到北韓開峰郡嘅一個邊境小<span style=\"color: red;\">鎮</span><br />\n見到有學校 有人 有屋企 仲見到有北韓人岀嚟散步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去江華島睇呢個仲值得 肉眼睇好細粒 但有望遠鏡 同成班朋友睇到唔想走</blockquote>"},{"pid":"27b5db2f1bc3d8ed7e22d009f4fdd3d081929ffc","tid":2071210,"uid":180745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"細個有去過南韓個邊<br />\n睇隧道 唔可以亂影相 望到北韓勁乾旱咁 咩都冇<br />\n但冇咩印象有生死狀呢樣野"},{"pid":"f884208c05ec14a3af77e75e66988265c9257181","tid":2071210,"uid":168020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/um8vKCh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fum8vKCh.png&h=89c97b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江華島瞭望台（紅色牌係瞭望台位置） <br />\n<br />\n呢邊