r />\nItinerary: Lotte Hotel Pick up &ndash; War Memorial Museum - Lunch &ndash; ID Check Point &ndash; Camp Bonifas (Slides Show and Briefing) &ndash; JSA (Freedom House, Conference Room, Bridge of no Return) &ndash; Arrive at Lotte Hotel.<br />\n我果時朝早車你去,去一個 War Memorial Museum, 睇果部中晒子彈既火車,最正應該係去JSA, 俾你入藍屋,間屋係一半係南韓,一半係北韓,所以都叫入左北韓領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最得意係會叫你影相鏡頭只可以向北韓,唔可以向韓,驚你唔覺意影左D事設施俾北韓既人知道左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去左咁多次旅行都仲係覺得DMZ係最難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26da821ab66e4628aac38294459dd2c7524d3805","tid":2071210,"uid":23120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9uzw4D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9uzw4D.png&h=fa6c0d64&s={SIZE}\" />入埋間屋，對面有個人渣住枝槍，中間隻窗望出去過左條界"},{"pid":"9fba44d3cd5ecf3bba9efc2fa67339560b02c6a0","tid":2071210,"uid":227804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"去北韓嘅時候去過 喺果度柯左duk屎 同埋同北韓軍人拍左張照"},{"pid":"f3b81549d8692fe02087c016840142c21ef5aebe","tid":2071210,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e70dd6065fd9af438b76c9a88b4ceb0acb4797","tid":2071210,"uid":119767,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"以前study tour 有跟學校去 DMZ<br />\n係有條地洞路<br />\n行到一個位就唔行得<br />\n話再行過去就係北韓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"去過地洞<br />\n行到死睇隻窗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0c1c09e05f620fe24117b23877436d987b085c","tid":2071210,"uid":178192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"去過 係南韓果邊去 <br />\n導遊話平時佢唔會去到邊界但果次放行比佢<br />\n好多規矩叫你唔好做<br />\n屋仔叫行入北韓果邊<br />\n果時仲見到北韓果邊啲遊客仲有軍人<br />\n應該係難得地先見到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c49GX8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc49GX8n.jpg&h=ee7a8f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBMVh8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBMVh8o.jpg&h=51c1195f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84b82a6e5d1e3d52a1dea2901723fd651fda4f12","tid":2071210,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26da821ab66e4628aac38294459dd2c7524d3805","tid":2071210,"uid":23120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9uzw4D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9uzw4D.png&h=fa6c0d64&s={SIZE}\" />入埋間屋，對面有個人渣住枝槍，中間隻窗望出去過左條界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好有戰地feel"},{"pid":"78006be7db68d64420c330f320cecc9cef1c9bae","tid":2071210,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:39:32.000Z","msg":"3年前去過"},{"pid":"c75f581d15cbad2703318aa2363dc2a7f78ac289","tid":2071210,"uid":326700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdf4580638cdab8adbcc334fb200429259cd346f","tid":2071210,"uid":112813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d78fee902a17fe25351c60954778710ddc4649c2","tid":2071210,"uid":168020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1449d0fb8157a247c5108c56581c6ec3adafecf9","tid":2071210,"uid":112813,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"跟團去北韓時去過<br />\n入去前有一大堆舖頭比你買野，之後上旅遊巴，有個北韓軍人上車企係車頭望住前面，話保護團友安全，落車入屋仔，屋入面有地圖，屋入面個北韓軍人係咁講美國衰野，之後就睇同坐簽約張枱同櫈，然後上板門店望條38線，對面南韓揀建築物靚過香港既好撚多<br />\n最on9係我個日唔小心著件有美帝國旗既衫比導遊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要搵件褸禁住先去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"巴打真係夠膽著呢啲 T-shirt 去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"我真係唔覺意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩個時秋天著返件縷都唔標奇立異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得你返到嚟已經係奇蹟"},{"pid":"69965641ca4e7c395f91db6077920cc18c1fc697","tid":2071210,"uid":196335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"其實已經變左旅遊景點，當地有旅行團報。"},{"pid":"115ea0ef8a7c159d40f69181086ee4221bf23aee","tid":2071210,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91421b407abb59b61e5ad742271d9ca5b3aac43","tid":2071210,"uid":168010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c75f581d15cbad2703318aa2363dc2a7f78ac289","tid":2071210,"uid":326700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdf4580638cdab8adbcc334fb200429259cd346f","tid":2071210,"uid":112813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d78fee902a17fe25351c60954778710ddc4649c2","tid":2071210,"uid":168020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"巴打真係夠膽著呢啲 T-shirt 去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"我真係唔覺意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩個時秋天著返件縷都唔標奇立異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得你返到嚟已經係奇蹟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"呢個真,咁大個人都唔撚用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06f2e2838900fbc9a04faa346991bd32fa4d927","tid":2071210,"uid":168010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"去幾次韓國都無去<br />\n下次MARK低記得去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08046e485146ab98c2d38e632cbb01d62399c368","tid":2071210,"uid":21383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"上年去過，但係嗰咁啱有啲軍事活動。去到出發前兩個星期先至有得去。喺南韓駐守嗰啲美軍話簽完板門店宣言後雙方撤軍後感覺冇咁緊張。成件事都幾輕鬆。不過我諗最近應該去唔到。南北韓關係最近都幾緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd1ba0e707d3b74233f556377f6682efbf79aea","tid":2071210,"uid":182885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"南韓北韓個邊都去過<br />\n<br />\n其實跟旅行團好易去"},{"pid":"5912a7361429be518ae9fb2d23cbc68f56b1b5d3","tid":2071210,"uid":353851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:24:44.000Z","msg":"6年前毒L一個自己去韓國旅行，膽粗粗去報板門店tour<br />\n唔少當地旅行社都有開團，但有英文導遊、又肯去到先收錢嘅就得一間<br />\n其他幾間一係只有日文導遊，一係可能太多人放飛機，要提供信用卡number俾佢記賬，實在唔放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果就報唯一呢間，有英文日文導遊各一，出發當日朝早喺旅行社check in先碌卡過數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個團包朝早入板門店，車程只係個零鐘(可見首爾市中心離南北韓真係好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，但要檢查兩次，兼有一次briefing，即係簽生死狀嘅時候，所以前後都用一整個朝早<br />\n中午喺DMZ外圍啲專做旅遊團嘅郊區餐廳仔食牛肉鍋，團餐來講唔算差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下午就去DMZ內幾個普通團都去到嘅景點(臨津閣、第一隧道、都羅山站)<br />\n<br />\n雖然團費唔平，成13萬圜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但真心值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由美軍帶隊參觀板門店，對面就係北韓，解說講到有大量歷史事件喺度發生過，能夠親身體驗歷史嘅感覺，非筆墨所能形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係獨遊嘅朋友，強烈推介夾時間報板門店團<br />\n一來唔係經常開到團，下次去未必夾到<br />\n二來其他旅伴如果對歷史無興趣，就算去到現場，感受都無自己去體會咁深"}]}